Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.47,IN_C_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,疑问？是愚问！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:25.81,IN_C_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,废话少说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:30.46,IN_C_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,吃下我全身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:32.27,IN_C_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,满载的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:34.57,IN_C_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,枪林弹雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:42.29,IN_C_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能牵起他人之手帮助他人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:47.13,IN_C_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,坚定所选Futurism
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:52.10,IN_C_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,一同经历的过去将为我指路
