Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快去安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧　艾尔芙娜茵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　响你也要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼　你到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊　未来和艾尔芙娜茵…
