Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:55.47,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(1031,449.001)}EPISODE 06
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:55.47,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(1030.666,502)}异语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现场周遭并没有遗体的目击报告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当地的医院也没有伤者送入的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那个出血量的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进一步扩大搜索范围
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手法相当缜密　绝非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕不是被意外波及
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　应该是敌人刻意设下的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟两个最高保护等级的人同时…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精通炼金术的后勤人员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和推断能够寄宿神之力的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查部本应对其加以保护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但偏偏被抓了受监察干扰的空当
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:04:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的目标是未来还是艾尔芙娜茵　抑或…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两者同为目标也不无可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论如何　收集情报都是当务之急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请继续进行搜索　希望能够打破僵局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴定结果就快出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查部定将全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位　一定要平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你　克利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来　那果然是佯动　连我都想到了Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时要是不理会管制指令的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月读　晓　你们是想说我对局势的判断有误吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉　不是这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下心里最难受的人都还在坚守岗位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意形象啊　前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了　这可不像你作风
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话都还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这状态怎么看都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是玻璃心碎一地Death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊　不过你们也都别再说她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她自己应该也是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我们也都知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将从护腕中抽出的奔涌能量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以限制器加以控制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们也就可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦妮莎　米蕾娅克带着客人回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的准备也很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神之力将为我们夺回未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚这错都在我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是与大家起争执
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是没能守护住弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是翼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尔之失态吾已耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无言以对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回定尽防人之责
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻印　掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼　此处实乃尔之战场乎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身居于此所守何物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又终守得何物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若觉前路迷茫　家门随时敞开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尔乃风鸣之世子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天羽羽斩乃为国镇灾祛邪之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切要铭记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的战场…不在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将召开紧急对策会议
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装者请速至司令部集合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼　你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就未来与艾尔芙娜茵失踪一事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基于最新调查报告召开紧急对策会议
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据鉴定结果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:08:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现场的血迹不是未来小姐和艾尔芙娜茵小姐两人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那未来和艾尔芙娜茵…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然没有遗体的目击报告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那比起被杀害　我们更有理由相信是被敌人绑架了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没到完全放心的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也总归是看到了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这么说的话　那一大滩血又是谁的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们仍在继续调查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后的主要目标就此改为救回二人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思　我可以提个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说绑架的话　掌握着炼金术的艾尔芙娜茵姑且不提
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那未来小姐又是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于未来为什么会被波及
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却未被杀害而是被绑架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前我们推断的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也该让你们知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人　欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自打来了日本我就一直想说说看来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是蒂福日城…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R\b0\pos(681.667,665.667)}Château de Tiffauges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要善待客人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就从下次开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呣(๑•ૅω•´๑)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真想想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在到底是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被带到这里之前发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔芙娜茵　没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔芙娜茵是那个跑得慢的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是会到处乱窜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想对我的朋友出手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊　未来小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到这么简单就把你带出了总部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在这
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要带走的只有艾尔芙娜茵一人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外一个的话我可管不了那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦妮莎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事要告诉米蕾娅克哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑　艾尔芙娜茵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来小姐　不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的　我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不要怪我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔芙娜茵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来小姐　你快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视上都看不到这样的场景了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经按耐不住全身的骚动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来小姐　快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到竟是这样的…天空景致
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了　未来小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来小姐在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个我们判断已经没用的人不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们留了她一条命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你们要利用摆脱了混乱诅咒的未来小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于你　也一样有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在需要你用这副卡萝尔的身体来启动一点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡萝尔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是这蒂福日城？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R\b0\pos(699.889,663)}Château de Tiffauges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便成功启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下既没有{\fnNirmala UI\fs50\fscx125}य{\fsp-7.5} {\fsp-0}न्{\fsp-9.5} {\fsp-0}त्{\fsp-9.5} {\fsp-0}र  स{\fsp-7.5} {\fsp-0}र्{\fsp-9.5} {\fsp-0}व{\fsp-7.5} {\fsp-0}स्{\fsp-9.5} {\fsp-0}व{\r}又没有Nephilim的左臂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(542,668.667)}<機械裝置百科事典>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是绝对无法正常操控的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想的那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让你启动的是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有点像是什么发生器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底是在图谋什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会坠落到哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不赶快回去的话　会让响担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了　我还要和响和好来着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的事件把非战斗人员也卷了进来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对大家的打击应该都不小
Comment: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她应该受了不小的打击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到那个时候被神兽镜照射了的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然摆脱了人类的原罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为可以寄宿神之力的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在努力尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用坚强的内心去接受这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对焦虑不安的翼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知道该如何去帮助她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说闹别扭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我和塞莲娜之间也有过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间总是充满了歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无需只言片语就能和好如初
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么好像最近在哪听到过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查结果全部在这里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认验收无误
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带着物证马上出发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被怀疑倒没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但拿到物证的话就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过监视网发现了S.O.N.G.的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们与风鸣机关之间的联系可能暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确定了地点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没什么好犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只能这么做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时只能让大姐姐我去突袭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个会继续进行神之力的具现化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　按照技研解析的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在垃圾处理厂回收的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,119.6％可以确定是安迪基西拉齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs25\pos(797.778,666.667)}O γρανάζι των Αντικυθήρων{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证真的数值反倒夸张到像是造假陷害了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先前事故中遗失的圣遗物却在敌人基地找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并没有接到物品被夺走的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是诈称遗失背地里交予他人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自护灾法实施以来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(581.555,670.333)}护国灾害派遣法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国内的圣遗物管理全部移交给风鸣机关了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如司令所怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镰仓和高傲之深红之间果然有所…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(561.556,670.333)}Noble Red
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有敌情　应该是为抢夺物证而来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都特意邀请你们了　居然不理人家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经安排救援过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她们抵达前一定要撑住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正有此意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对撞机 SWITCH ON
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现代忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:38.33,IN_C_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}Killter ichaival tron
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:24.70,IN_C_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ichaival和{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs55}Airgetlámh{\r}与敌人交战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漏洞百出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是用这些卑鄙手段
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认绪川先生已经脱离战场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人高傲之深红乘着一般车辆开始移动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(478,670.333)}Noble Red
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消灭物证失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能先拖住装者们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又准备把一般人卷进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你休想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs55}Airgetlámh{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们姐妹对这光芒也是不管不问就都敢往身上穿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊拉克战争时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美军接收的圣遗物之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与Shul-shagana和Igalima不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因来历不明为便于称呼起了名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但正体全然不明的神秘Gear
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逗你玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是她们惯用的小伎俩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让她给你带跑了节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再让你为所欲为了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看世界的尽头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这样又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就先交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们的无能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要徒增无辜的受害者咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这时直击弱点也是同样结果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也瞄得太没谱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Put your hands up 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出被你们绑走的未来和艾尔芙娜茵的下落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂福日城…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R\b0\pos(622.556,667)}Château de Tiffauges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显现？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这也太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我听来就是「apple」啊
